timing_report_..._message_types(25.10)  timing_report_..._message_types(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_redirect_message_types

Syntax
       timing_report_redirect_message_types

       {none | info}

       Default: none

       Redirects reporting messages to a report file.

       When  set to info, the path count and max depth (displayed when the re-
       port_timing command is run in PBA mode) will be appended to  the  final
       report output.

       When set to none, the reporting messages are not redirected to a report
       file.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

